@node Distribution "Distribution"
@{par}@{b}Distribution@{ub}
@{par}~~~~~~~~~~~~
@{par}This program is Giftware.  Feel free to give it to your friends, force it on
your enemies or feed it to your dog (but only if you've first transferred it
to some suitably edible media). If you really like this program, feel free to
send me any form of gift (money, disks, bug reports, parcelbombs etc), or
just an email to let me know that you like the program. If you send me an
email address, I'll try to keep you informed of any updates or other programs
that I write.
@{par}
@{par}This archive can be placed on Aminet, and any similar free-access FTP sites,
BBSs, Aminet CDs and Fred Fish's AmigaLibrary.
It can be included in other public domain collections, provided that charges
made are minimal (I would suggest no more than Ł1.50 per floppy, Ł15 per CD)
You can also include it on the coverdisk/CD of a magazine provided that you
send me a copy.
@{par}
@{par}The latest version of this, and any other programs I have written, can be
found using the World Wide Web at:
@{par}
@{par}http://users.ox.ac.uk/~kebl0206/mrjsw/
@endnode

