@node History "History"
@{par}@{b}History@{ub}
@{par}~~~~~~~
@{par}v1.00  First release. 'nuff said.
@{par}
@{par}v1.01  Erm....  I changed the name and ... and ...
@{par}
@{par}v1.02  Fixed to work with any size title font.
@{par}
@{par}v1.10  First test of new window system.
@{par}
@{par}v1.11  Vaguely working version.
@{par}
@{par}v1.12  Fully working version (except for blink).
@{par}
@{par}v1.13  Abort window move/size with right mouse button.
@{par}
@{par}v1.14  Blinking functional, memory usage much lower.
@{par}
@{par}v1.15  Blinking now fully adjustable in five ways.
@{par}
@{par}v1.20  GUI options window, installs as commodity.
@{par}
@{par}v1.21  Options can now be used and saved.
@{par}
@{par}v1.22  All options can be changed 'on the fly'.
@{par}
@{par}v1.23  Colours can be changed, background snapped.
@{par}
@{par}v1.24  Palette added to redsigned GUI.
@{par}
@{par}v1.25  Eyes can be dis-/enabled.
@{par}
@{par}v1.26  GUI resizing etc smoothed and speeded up
@{par}
@{par}v2.00  Second Release.
@{par}
@{par}v2.01  Runtime error debugger disabled -> smaller executables
@endnode
